{"tid":2498771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲取消維州與中國簽署兩項有關「一帶一路」合作協議","createTime":"2021-04-21T11:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T08:37:25.000Z","uid":179729,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ca51825e87e1170f63fa6adea40ff528fed0c050","tid":2498771,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1586977_1_20210421192323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1586977_1_20210421192323.jpg&h=aeabdd43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲外長佩恩表示，澳洲已經取消維多利亞州與中國簽署的兩項有關「一帶一路」合作協議，原因是協議與澳洲的外交政策不一致，或者不利澳洲的外交關係。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，根據一項新程序，佩恩能夠審查澳洲各州和大學與外國達成的協議。<br />\n<br />\n佩恩發表聲明說，她已決定取消四項協議，包括維多利亞州在2018年和2019年與中國達成的兩項協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586977-20210421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586977-20210421.htm&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=62d5fc98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586977-20210421.htm&h=d2f11ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586977-20210421.htm</a>"},{"pid":"55fd7e4b1677616fe0b6d40029e879e74de19787","tid":2498771,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fac4997225ac345860e83eb84c2ea48f6cc8308","tid":2498771,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"澳洲好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c543b263b3031da110d201ea0cce1255d34b24e","tid":2498771,"uid":60924,